OL,3,CWoman dies after alligator bites her
OL,4,Carm off in Florida
OL,6,FA string of alligator attacks across
OL,7,Fcentral Florida has left multiple
OL,8,Fpeople injured, with the most recent
OL,9,Fattack killing a 31-year-old woman who
OL,10,Fhad one of her arms bitten off.
OL,12,FSerious encounters with alligators are
OL,13,Frelatively rare, according to Florida
OL,14,FFish and Wildlife Conservation
OL,15,FCommission data (FWC), but there have
OL,16,Fbeen three attacks in the state over
OL,17,Fthe past week.
OL,19,FTwo of them came within 24 hours of
OL,20,Feach other, according to ITV News' US
OL,21,Fpartner CNN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
