CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782857895
OL,3,CWoman dies after alligator bites her
OL,4,Carm off in Florida
OL,6,FThe victim of the latest attack had
OL,7,Freportedly been swimming with her
OL,8,Fboyfriend and friend in the
OL,9,FEconlockhatchee River, just north of
OL,10,FOrlando, on Sunday afternoon before
OL,11,Fthe alligator attacked her.
OL,13,FOfficials said that her boyfriend had
OL,14,Ftried to pull her out of the
OL,15,Falligator's mouth. She had suffered
OL,16,Fbites to both her arms and later died
OL,17,Fwhile being taken to the hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
