PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782857895
OL,3,CWoman dies after alligator bites her
OL,4,Carm off in Florida
OL,6,FFWC officials captured a 13-foot
OL,7,Falligator at the scene, and a 12-
OL,8,Ffooter nearby, and both are having
OL,9,Ftheir DNA tested to see who could have
OL,10,Fbeen responsible for the attack.
OL,12,FFlorida is home to an estimated 1.3
OL,13,Fmillion alligators, but attacks on
OL,14,Fpeople remain uncommon.
OL,16,FAn average of around eight unprovoked
OL,17,Fbites occurs each year, according to
OL,18,Ffigures. Since 1948, Florida has
OL,19,Frecorded more than 450 alligator
OL,20,Fattacks, with only 30 resulting in
OL,21,Ffatalities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
