PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782857895
OL,3,CWoman dies after alligator bites her
OL,4,Carm off in Florida
OL,6,FThe highest number of fatal attacks
OL,7,Foccur when people deliberately enter
OL,8,Fwaterways known to contain alligators.
OL,10,FHow dangerous are alligators to humans?
OL,12,FAmerican alligators are dangerous apex
OL,13,Fpredators, capable of inflicting
OL,14,Fsevere or even fatal injuries on
OL,15,Fhumans.
OL,17,FBut fatal attacks are extremely rare.
OL,18,FAlligators naturally fear humans and
OL,19,Ftypically retreat when approached.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
