OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782857895
OL,3,CWoman dies after alligator bites her
OL,4,Carm off in Florida
OL,6,FMost attacks from alligators happen
OL,7,Fnear water, where alligators can use
OL,8,Fstealth to sneak up on their prey.
OL,10,FSmall pets or dogs are frequently
OL,11,Fmistaken for natural prey by
OL,12,Falligators and bring them into closer
OL,13,Fproximity to their owners.
